5 200 feet in height, as measured from the natural ground level at the base of the tower to the middle of the
6 turbine rotor hub.
7
8 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Codification instruction. [Sections 1 through 3] are intended to be
9 codified as an integral part of Title 75, chapter 26, and the provisions of Title 75, chapter 26, apply to [sections
10 1 through 3].
11
12 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Effective date. [This act] is effective January 1, 2026.
